         <abstract>
            <p>The purpose of this article is to introduce the on-line Intermediate Latin Program to potential users by describing the goals and elements of the site (see www.iona.edu/latin). The operation of the program is described in full, as well as its benefits for language education, its current uses, and suggestions for more creative uses in the classroom. Included throughout the article are observations on the program made by students, faculty, the design team, and assessors.</p>
         </abstract>
